Subject: [PATCH] feat: Implement skeleton screens for a premium loading
 experience

This commit replaces the existing loading spinners with skeleton screens to prov
ide a more premium and user-friendly loading experience. Skeleton screens show a
 placeholder preview of the content, which gives the user a better sense of what
's to come.

- Replaced `Loader2` components with `Skeleton` components in the main dashboard
 layouts and key dashboard tabs.
- Designed the skeleton screens to mimic the layout of the content being loaded.
